{"questionId":"12221","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;= <strong><em>M</em></strong> where <strong><em>M</em></strong> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;b \\\\   c&amp;d  \\end{array}} \\right){\\text{,}}\\,\\,bc \\ne 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>c</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>d</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.&nbsp;</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p class=\"indent2\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;\">Show that (<strong><em>I</em></strong> − <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;= <strong><em>I</em></strong> − <strong><em>M</em></strong> where <strong><em>I</em></strong> is the identity matrix.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>Attempting to expand (<strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>M1 </strong></em></p>\n<p>(<strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;= <strong><em>I</em></strong> − 2<strong><em>M</em></strong> + <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = <strong><em>I</em></strong> − 2<strong><em>M</em></strong> + <strong><em>M</em></strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = <strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>AG&nbsp; &nbsp;N0 </strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>Attempting to expand (<strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {1 - a}&amp;{ - b} \\\\   { - c}&amp;{1 - d}  \\end{array}} \\right)^2}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>c</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>d</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; (or equivalent)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>(<strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {{{\\left( {1 - a} \\right)}^2} + bc}&amp;{ - b\\left( {1 - a} \\right) - b\\left( {1 - d} \\right)} \\\\   { - c\\left( {1 - a} \\right) - c\\left( {1 - d} \\right)}&amp;{bc + {{\\left( {1 - d} \\right)}^2}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mo>(</mo>\n                      <mrow>\n                        <mn>1</mn>\n                        <mo>−</mo>\n                        <mi>a</mi>\n                      </mrow>\n                      <mo>)</mo>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>d</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>d</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mo>(</mo>\n                      <mrow>\n                        <mn>1</mn>\n                        <mo>−</mo>\n                        <mi>d</mi>\n                      </mrow>\n                      <mo>)</mo>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>(or equivalent)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1 &nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p>Use of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a + d = 1\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"bc = a - {a^2}\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;to show desired result.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>Hence&nbsp;(<strong><em>I</em></strong>&nbsp;− <strong><em>M</em></strong>)<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {1 - a}&amp;{ - b} \\\\   { - c}&amp;{1 - d}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>d</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>AG&nbsp; &nbsp;N0</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12221","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.22d","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Show that (I − M)2 = I − M where I is the identity matrix.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"d","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}